headline.main: Fitzgerald Scores Tournament-Record 30 as Temple Advances
headline.print_headline: Fitzgerald Scores Tournament-Record 30 as Temple Advances

lead_paragraph: A goal by Ellen White, a substitute, in the 89th minute at the SheBelieves Cup lifted England to only its fourth win in 14 games against the United States.
